high_descs: Walk towards the tub, then hang a right and walk up to the small white dresser.
Pick up the closest blue spray bottle off of the dresser.
Walk over to the silver bin next to the toilet behind you.
Put the blue spray bottle in the bin.
Turn right and walk over to the small white dresser next to the sink.
Pick up the blue spray bottle off of the dresser.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk over to the other wall, turn right again to face the toilet and look down at the silver bin next to the toilet.
Put the blue spray bottle in the silver bin.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles into a silver bin.

high_descs: Turn to the white end table on your right.
Pick up the blue spray bottle closest to the edge of the end table.
Turn around and go to the garbage can on the floor, to the left of the toilet.
Place the blue spray bottle in the garbage can.
Turn around and go back to the end table across from you.
Pick up the other blue spray bottle from the end table.
Turn around and go back to the garbage can on the floor, to the left of the toilet.
Place the blue spray bottle in the garbage can, to the right of the other one.
anns.task_desc: Put two spray bottles in the bathroom garbage.

high_descs: Turn right then face the cabinet on the right
Pick up the first spray bottle in front of you
Turn right then head to the left side of the trash bin
Put the spray bottle in the trash bin
Turn right and head back to the cabinet
Pick up the spray bottle
Turn right then head to the trash bin
Put the spray bottle in the trash bin
anns.task_desc: Put the two spray bottles in the trash bin
